To add custom images for weapons:
Place these PNG files in assets/images/:

bullet_player.png - Yellow/small bullet

bullet_enemy.png - Red/small bullet

missile_player.png - Orange missile shape

missile_enemy.png - Red missile shape

powerup_double.png - Cyan star

powerup_triple.png - Yellow star

powerup_laser.png - Purple star

powerup_shield.png - Blue star

powerup_health.png - Green star

powerup_missile.png - Orange star

powerup_speed.png - Red star

powerup_magnet.png - White star

powerup_life.png - Gold star